high_descs: Take a few steps right to face the counter.
Pick up the red cloth from the counter.
Move a few steps to the right and face the sink.
Place the cloth in the sink. Turn the water on and off. Take the cloth back out of the sink.
Take the cloth and take a few steps to the right to face the other sink.
Open the top drawer and place the cloth inside. Shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Rinse off a cloth and put it away in a drawer.

high_descs: turn right, then turn left to face the bathroom sink counter top
pick up the red wash cloth on the table
place the red wash cloth in the sink basin
turn on the faucet and fill the sink with water, then remove the red wash cloth
face the white drawer beneath the counter top on the far right hand side
open the drawer and put the red wash cloth inside, then close the drawer
anns.task_desc: Rinse the wash cloth and store it away in a drawer

high_descs: turn to the right towards the sink area
pick up the dirty rag from the sink table
turn to the right put it inside the sink
rinse the rag off on the sink
open the bottom cabinet of the sink table put the rag inside of it
anns.task_desc: rinse off a dirty rag put it inside of the bottom drawer of the sink table
